title: Nuts Magazine Collection May 31 - July 25 2013 - AfT3RLiF3
description:
This is a personal collection of NUTS Magazine from me AfT3RLiF3 from the months of May 31st - July 25th to finish the new year.. Hope you enjoy

Nuts is a weekly lad mag published in the United Kingdom. 
It was the first weekly lads magazine to be published in the
UK and is sold every Tuesday (originally every Thursday). 
Nuts marketing campaign uses a slogan, "When You Really Need Something Funny".
